text: Sigfrid Larsson (1 January 1882 - 9 October 1968) was a Swedish diver. He competed in two events at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:1968 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
